OL,3,CProbe into bans for Grenfell firms
OL,4,Cpaused amidst criminal investigation
OL,6,FInvestigations into banning firms
OL,7,Fcriticised in the Grenfell Tower
OL,8,FInquiry have been paused "to prevent
OL,9,Fany impact on criminal investigations".
OL,11,FThe Cabinet office confirmed in
OL,12,FFebruary that seven companies were
OL,13,Ffacing possible bans from public
OL,14,Fcontracts.
OL,16,FThey are cladding firm Arconic,
OL,17,Finsulation firm Kingspan, former
OL,18,FCelotex owners Saint-Gobain, fire
OL,19,Finspectors Exova, design and build
OL,20,Fcontractor Rydon, architect Studio E
OL,21,Fand subcontractor Harley Facades.
