OL,3,CProbe into bans for Grenfell firms
OL,4,Cpaused amidst criminal investigation
OL,6,FAll faced criticism in the final
OL,7,Freport of the inquiry into the June
OL,8,F2017 west London tower block fire,
OL,9,Fwhich claimed the lives of 72 people.
OL,11,FInvestigations were believed to have
OL,12,Fbeen launched into all of them in
OL,13,FMarch, looking into whether any
OL,14,Fengaged in professional misconduct for
OL,15,Fthe purposes of the Procurement Act
OL,16,F2023, potentially leading them to be
OL,17,Fdebarred from public contracts.
OL,19,FBut the Government said it had paused
OL,20,Fits investigations so as not to impact
OL,21,Fon criminal investigations.
