OL,3,CProbe into bans for Grenfell firms
OL,4,Cpaused amidst criminal investigation
OL,6,FIn a statement published on Thursday,
OL,7,Fit said: "The Metropolitan Police and
OL,8,FCrown Prosecution Service informed the
OL,9,FCabinet Office that continuing the
OL,10,Fdebarment investigations could
OL,11,Funintentionally prejudice the criminal
OL,12,Finvestigation and any future criminal
OL,13,Fproceedings.
