OL,3,CProbe into bans for Grenfell firms
OL,4,Cpaused amidst criminal investigation
OL,6,F"To ensure the Metropolitan Police's
OL,7,Fcriminal investigation and any future
OL,8,Fproceedings remain the priority, the
OL,9,FCabinet Office has paused its
OL,10,Fseparate, non-criminal debarment
OL,11,Finvestigations at the request of the
OL,12,FCrown Prosecution Service (CPS) and
OL,13,Fthe Metropolitan Police. This decision
OL,14,Fhas been made to safeguard the
OL,15,Fintegrity of the Metropolitan Police's
OL,16,Fcriminal investigation."
OL,18,FThe CPS said it had noted the
OL,19,FGovernment's decision to pause
OL,20,Fdebarment investigations.
