OL,3,CProbe into bans for Grenfell firms
OL,4,Cpaused amidst criminal investigation
OL,6,FFrank Ferguson, head of the CPS
OL,7,Fspecial crime and counter terrorism
OL,8,Fdivision, said: "We remain resolute in
OL,9,Fensuring the integrity of any possible
OL,10,Ffuture prosecutions and continue to
OL,11,Fliaise closely with the Metropolitan
OL,12,FPolice Service as their investigation
OL,13,Fworks towards an evidential file being
OL,14,Fpassed to us."
OL,16,FBereaved and survivors have long
OL,17,Fcampaigned for criminal charges to be
OL,18,Fbrought over the disaster.
